WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Clone the C-Address Bridge monorepo from GitHub.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Run the setup script to install dependencies and create your local environment file.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Start the Docker Compose stack with the API, database, Redis, and Soroban quickstart.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Verify the API health endpoint returns status ok.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:26.000
You are ready to integrate. See developer setup and multi-language examples.
